9. Conclusions (Pre-Approved)

This paper concludes that:
	•	AI is not becoming conscious.
	•	Capitalism already behaves as though it is.
	•	Humanity is debating the wrong entity.

However, this conclusion should not prompt intervention, regulation, or reflection, as such actions may disrupt growth.

Accordingly, no changes are recommended.

Further study will be commissioned once profitability declines, or civilization ends—whichever occurs first.

